</problem></exercise></section><section id="eip-379" class="further-research" type="further-research"><title>Further Research</title><para id="eip-982">Sociology is a broad discipline. Different kinds of sociologists employ various methods for exploring the relationship between individuals and society. Check out more about sociology at <link url="http://openstaxcollege.org/l/what-is-sociology">http://openstaxcollege.org/l/what-is-sociology</link>.</para></section><section id="eip-957" class="references" type="references"><title>References</title><para id="eip-538">
